Name: Ipp percentage
Description: Inductor ripple current percentage (with respect to average inductor current)

Name: Noise limits defined by CISPR Standards
Description: Noise limits for CLASS 5 of CISPR 25 standard

Name: Input Ripple Noise before input filter
Description: Input Ripple Noise before filter at switching frequency

Name: Input Ripple Noise After input filter
Description: Input Ripple Noise after filter at switching frequency

Name: FootPrint
Description: Total Foot Print Area of BOM components

Name: Vout Actual
Description: Vout Actual calculated based on selected voltage divider resistors

Name: Vout Tolerance
Description: Vout Tolerance based on IC Tolerance (no load) and voltage divider resistors if applicable
